snippet.title: The Red Light District of Blackpool
snippet.description:
**Filmed October 30th 2020 during Tier 3 restrictions**

I return to Cookson Street in Blackpool town centre to follow up on my hugely popular red light district vlog filmed back in the summer of 2020. In this video I expand a little on how the massage parlours/saunas are allowed to operate in this area, as well as finding a couple of new places I did not cover on the first video.

Please check out these Amazon links to the gear I use for my videos....
DJI Osmo Camera https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B07KVV1W5S/ref=as_sl_pc_qf_sp_asin_til?tag=starman1969-21&linkCode=w00&linkId=18080d35f2a846c09634f173f518e3b0&creativeASIN=B07KVV1W5S
DJI Mavic Mini Drone https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B07RRMPZ4L/ref=as_sl_pc_qf_sp_asin_til?tag=starman1969-21&linkCode=w00&linkId=5f2f1488380d18c1c79404e8baf8cfb3&creativeASIN=B07RRMPZ4L
Boya lav microphone https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B00MN69744/ref=as_sl_pc_qf_sp_asin_til?tag=starman1969-21&linkCode=w00&linkId=7682b291dba08b55258f23e8b9c4c130&creativeASIN=B00MN69744

A Walk on the Wild Side merch here: https://teespring.com/en-GB/stores/a-walk-on-the-wild-side

Music: looperman.com
